### Customer Service API Requests (Port 8081)

### Create Customer
POST http://localhost:8081/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phone": "555-0101",
  "address": "123 Main St, City"
}

### Get All Customers
GET http://localhost:8081/customers

### Get Customer by ID
GET http://localhost:8081/customers/1

### Update Customer
PUT http://localhost:8081/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "email": "john.updated@example.com",
  "phone": "555-0199",
  "address": "456 New St, City"
}

### Delete Customer
DELETE http://localhost:8081/customers/1

###############################################
### Account Service API Requests (Port 8082)
###############################################

### Create Account
POST http://localhost:8082/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "accountType": "SAVINGS",
  "initialBalance": 1000.00
}

### Get All Accounts
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts

### Get Account by ID
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/1

### Get Accounts by Customer ID
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/customer/1

### Update Account
PUT http://localhost:8082/accounts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "accountType": "CHECKING",
  "initialBalance": 1000.00
}

### Delete Account
DELETE http://localhost:8082/accounts/1

